Insert into OE.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTIONS (PRODUCT_ID,LANGUAGE_ID,TRANSLATED_NAME,TRANSLATED_DESCRIPTION) values (2412,'US','8MB EDO Memory','8 MB 8x32 EDO SIM memory. Extended Data Out memory differs from FPM in a small, but significant design change. Unlike FPM, the data output drivers for EDO remain on when the memory controller removes the column address to begin the next cycle. Therefore, a new data cycle can begin before the previous cycle has completed. EDO is available on SIMMs and DIMMs, in 3.3 and 5 volt varieties.');
